        {
            "title": "日本央行維持利率不變;警告通膨風險將推動更多升息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kFZog9b4zuuVf.OlHfW6MQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB1304I_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"日本央行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:日本央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/日本央行\">日本央行</a>週二如預期維持利率不變,但警告稱,由於中東戰爭的影響,經濟成長將放緩,通膨將上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行將隔夜拆款利率維持在0.75%。但此決定並非一致通過,該行9名利率決策委員會成員中有3人因通膨風險上升而呼籲提高利率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">央行表示,將\"繼續提高政策利率並調整貨幣寬鬆程度\",特別是在日本經濟面臨通膨風險上升的情況下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行在聲明中表示,預計2026財年消費者物價指數通膨率將遠高於最初預期。預計2026年整體CPI通膨率將在2.8%至3.0%之間,遠高於先前預測的1.9%至2.0%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8f477bf3-f13d-3ba9-9851-6db0fa6c0429-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不包括新鮮食品和能源價格的核心CPI預計在2026年將介於2.5%至2.7%之間,高於先前預測的2.0%至2.3%。該數據現在預計將更大幅度地超過日本央行2%的年度目標。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行表示,由於中東戰爭導致原油價格上漲的影響,日本2026財年的經濟成長可能會放緩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2026財年實質國內生產毛額現在預計將在0.4%至0.7%之間,而先前預測為0.8%至1.0%。日本央行也下調了2027和2028財年的預測。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行警告稱,石油和能源價格上漲可能會轉嫁給消費者並損害企業利潤,同時也會拖累經濟成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但日本央行表示,私人支出的強勁和穩定的企業利潤預計仍將有助於支撐未來幾年的成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自2024年初結束近十年的超寬鬆貨幣政策以來,該央行已累計加息85點子。市場普遍預期,央行將在未來幾個月進一步加息,特別是在面臨中東衝突引發的通膨風險加劇的情況下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%8D%87%E6%81%AF-042620798.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 12:47:12",
