        },
        {
            "title": "【新盤動態】黃金海灣．意嵐加推70伙｜折實均呎14,626元    加價約29%｜一房折實約426.6萬元起",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">旭日國際旗下黃金海灣．意嵐昨日（27日）公布第6號價單，加推70伙。新一批單位折實均呎為14,626元，較上一張價單大幅加價約29%。呎價上升主要由於發展商減少折扣，加上新價單包括天台特色戶，而且暫無同類單位可作直接比較，故這次推售屬於加價加推。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發展商定於本周五（5月1日）開售，當中一房連儲物室及5伙兩房戶，合共28伙，將以先到先得發售。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"黃金海灣．意嵐價單\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:黃金海灣．意嵐價單;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3PVfQyt\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">黃金海灣．意嵐價單</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"施政報告後發展商動作多多 長實3盤齊加價 黃金海灣·意嵐加推 DOUBLE COAST I預告開價\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:施政報告後發展商動作多多 長實3盤齊加價 黃金海灣·意嵐加推 DOUBLE COAST I預告開價;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4uebPnU\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">施政報告後發展商動作多多 長實3盤齊加價 黃金海灣·意嵐加推 DOUBLE COAST I預告開價</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>加推第6號價單共70伙     折實均呎14,626元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發展商昨日（27日）公布第6號價單，加推70個單位。新一批單位實用面積介乎300至516平方呎，涵蓋23個一房戶、33個兩房戶，以及14個連天台特色戶。若按定價計算，整批單位市值約4.26億元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1be74fe4-009c-3144-b3e3-e369ba18914e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對比2024年10月推出的上一張價單，新一批單位的最高折扣優惠由原來的12%大幅削減至3%。在扣除最高3%折扣後，這批單位的折實售價介乎426.6萬至831.7萬元，折實呎價約12,017至16,770元。整批折實均呎為14,626元，較第5號價單的11,336元高出約29%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次折實均呎明顯上升，主要有幾個原因。首先，發展商把折扣大減9%；其次，新價單加入了定價較高的天台特色戶。加上這次推出的單位，座數、方向與景觀都跟上一批不同，暫時沒有同類單位可以直接比較呎價。這幾個原因加起來，便拉高整體平均呎價，屬加價加推。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>一房折實入場費約426.6萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第6號價單中，一房入場單位為第5座（5A）5樓G室，單位連同衣帽間，實用面積355平方呎，折實售價約426.6萬元，折實呎價約12,017元，屬整批單位中呎價最低。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ajf0Rs9lwVukxTGwveTTjA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/787cdb4157d51dcfd5d1f2db6b33ac4c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>一房入場單位：第5座（5A）5樓G室平面圖</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房折實入場費約588.6萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩房入場單位則為第5座（5A）5樓B室，實用面積444平方呎，折實售價約588.6萬元，折實呎價約13,257元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VoXiWtPpzikfuVSXjxBjBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/2dfaa7c755884bad0fbe968f16fc2818\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房入場單位：第5座（5A）5樓B室平面圖</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於折實呎價最高的單位，是第5座（5A）26樓H室的天台特色戶，實用面積300平方呎，折實售價約503.1萬元，折實呎價約16,770元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>項目背景</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金海灣．意嵐位於屯門青山公路青山灣段18號，由旭日國際發展。項目共提供692伙，戶型由開放式至三房不等，並設有特色戶。校網方面，小學屬於71校網，中學則為屯門區。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Double Coast I\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:Double Coast I;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/double-coast-i\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Double Coast I</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Double Coast\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:Double Coast;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/Double-Coast-32878\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Double Coast</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"黃金海灣\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:黃金海灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/黃金海灣-28951\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">黃金海灣</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"屯門\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:屯門;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/屯門-27309\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">屯門</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%8B%95%E6%85%8B-%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A3-%E6%84%8F%E5%B5%90%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A870%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E14-626%E5%85%83-%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B9%E7%B4%8429-%E4%B8%80%E6%88%BF%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E7%B4%84426-6%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B5%B7-75734\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
